               kpred:last-push    "2026-07-14"^^xsd:date ;
               kpred:description  "Privacy-first, self-hosted, fully open-source personal knowledge management. Block-level references, self-hosted sync." ;
               kpred:closest-to   kb:core-product ;
               kpred:validates    "SELF-HOSTED SYNC, not hosted sync. It is proof that 'the user controls where their knowledge lives' and 'the knowledge syncs across my devices' are not in conflict — which is the strongest challenge to our current position that sync must simply be declined (kb:avoid-hosted-sync)." .

